06:07.000 --> 06:12.000
From then, the water is electrolyzed. We produce hydrogen and oxygen.

06:12.000 --> 06:15.000
Oxygen is vented and hydrogen is captured.

06:15.000 --> 06:19.000
It is then purified through our dryer and purifier.

06:19.000 --> 06:30.000
The purifier removes any trace oxygen inside hydrogen stream and the dryer removes any moisture that was left over from the electrolysis process.

06:30.000 --> 06:38.000
The gas comes out at about 150 psi from then on it's compressed to 6000 psi where it's stored into storage tanks.

06:38.000 --> 06:42.000
