07:22.000 --> 07:27.000
In a gasification system, we convert coal to something very similar to natural gas.

07:27.000 --> 07:37.000
Then that natural gas has an extremely high hydrogen content and we can then take that and either manipulate it to pure hydrogen or we can even produce liquid fuels from it.

07:37.000 --> 07:45.000
Gasification has the promise of being one of the few sources that we can use to produce very, very large quantities of hydrogen.

07:45.000 --> 07:52.000
So as we transition to a hydrogen economy, coal is one of those domestic resources that can really step in.

07:52.000 --> 07:56.000
