08:14.000 --> 08:17.000
Hydrogen today is something we look to for the future.

08:17.000 --> 08:27.000
If you want to talk about renewables, you've got to find a way in which to store the energy because electrical energy has to be used at the time it's produced.

08:28.000 --> 08:34.000
