08:34.000 --> 08:37.000
And so if you're producing it, how do we store it?

08:37.000 --> 08:40.000
The hydrogen concept is one of those opportunities.

08:49.000 --> 08:52.000
A hydrogen generation can happen through a number of different routes.

08:52.000 --> 09:01.000
