11:07.000 --> 11:16.000
Other renewable ways of making hydrogen is to capture solar, wind, wave, geothermal power and electrolyze water to produce hydrogen.

11:16.000 --> 11:24.000
We produce hydrogen in a very environmentally friendly way because of the fact that we have hydroelectric power.

11:24.000 --> 11:32.000
However, we have to transport that hydrogen and the transportation does have an impact in terms of the carbon footprint.

11:32.000 --> 11:38.000
The reason we liquefy hydrogen is it's perhaps the most sufficient way to distribute hydrogen over long distances.

11:38.000 --> 11:43.000
