11:43.000 --> 11:51.000
Currently, there's three traditional ways of storing hydrogen as largely dependent upon the volume of hydrogen you want to store

11:51.000 --> 11:54.000
and how far you want to transport it.

11:54.000 --> 12:00.000
So if you need a couple of kilograms of hydrogen, typically steel cylinders is what you would use.

12:00.000 --> 12:06.000
