15:08.000 --> 15:17.000
So instead of a pump that draws fluid out, you have a valving that opens and closes to control the flow of gas to the vehicle.

15:17.000 --> 15:25.000
Instead of a turbine meter and a gasoline dispenser that spins to give you a reading on volume,

15:25.000 --> 15:30.000
you have a mass flow meter which senses the molecules of hydrogen flowing through it

15:30.000 --> 15:33.000
and gives you that same mass reading on the display.

